35 Commissioner of St. Clair County, in addition to the
36 compensation the revenue commissioner received on May 31,
37 2026, shall receive an additional expense allowance in an
38 amount that brings the revenue commissioner's total annual
39 compensation to one hundred thirty thousand dollars
40 ($130,000).
41 (b) Commencing October 1, 2027, the total base annual
42 salary for the revenue commissioner shall be one hundred
43 thirty thousand dollars ($130,000), in lieu of all other
44 expense allowances and other forms of compensation.
45 Section 4. (a) Commencing June 1, 2026, the Chair of
46 the St. Clair County Commission, in addition to the
47 compensation the chair received on May 31, 2026, shall receive
48 an additional expense allowance in an amount that brings the
49 chair's total annual compensation to one hundred thirty
50 thousand dollars ($130,000).
51 (b) Commencing November 11, 2026, the total base annual
52 salary for the chair shall be one hundred thirty thousand
53 dollars ($130,000), in lieu of all other expense allowances
54 and other forms of compensation.
55 Section 5. (a) Commencing June 1, 2026, each non-chair
56 member of the St. Clair County Commission, in addition to the
